Home 

Home



Introducing our all NEW body art product lines!
We’re bringing a whole new level of excitement to wearables with our new gold & silver Metallic Temporary Tattoos & Jeweled Temporary Tattoos! All of our temporary tattoos are stylish & safe. Our metallic tattoos shimmer like jewelry, plus mix & match them for endless combinations. Jeweled tattoos add intriguing layers of dimension to your look in minutes. Create looks you’ll love EVERY time.
Mark Richards also proudly offers an extensive variety of canvas aprons, totes & novelties. We believe that Mark Richards has the finest quality of canvas items at the least expensive prices, and all our canvas is eco friendly. While we’re talking wearables, you will not want to miss our wide-ranging assortment of iron-ons or our gorgeous Fluerettes™ fabric flowers, feathers & bows available in a wide variety of materials, textures & popular themes. Our product line continuously evolves to keep you on trend with innovative, fashionable embellishments for all your creative needs.
We also offer the most complete and competitive assortment of adhesive rhinestone embellishments in the art, craft & wearables industries. Our Crystal Stickers® offer infinite versatility for paper crafting, altered arts, crafts, gifts, home décor, wearables and so much more. With a variety of styles like traditional crystal, pearl and glitter to stunningly arranged clusters, borders, and jewelry embellishments there are Crystal Stickers® for every project.
Mark Richards provides embellishment designs your customers desire, quality they deserve and the prices they expect. There are so many ways to create with Mark Richards.
